│ UB. Adding a bounds check to bail on out-of-range indices prevents the        │
│ transformation in such cases, preserving correctness. This fix is narrow,     │
│ safe, and aligned with existing design (early exits on unsafe patterns).      │
│ --------------------  END  --------------------                               │
